NTP to DCF77 converter for ESP8266. 

This code development on Platformio used by NTPClient library.
Only 1 second order sycronazation.

Please set the value in top of source code.

NTPSERVER - ntp server
TIMEOFFSET - time zone
DCF77OUT - DCF77 out pin
ssid[] - your wifi ssid
passwd[] - your wifi password

Output is 5 minutes and go deepsleep.
PON connect to Reset by condencer for wakeup.

This code is BSD licence.

